kerning:0pt">11</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">A</span></span><span lang="EN-USTimes" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：派生类构造函数必须对这三类成员进行初始化，其执行顺序：调用基类构造函数；调用子对象的构造函数；派生类的构造函数体。析构函数在执行过程中也要对基类和成员对象进行操作，但它的执行过程与构造函数正好相反，即对派生类新增普通成员进行清理；调用成员对象析构函数，对派生类新增的成员对象进行清理；调用基类析构函数，对基类进行清理，所以选择<span lang="EN-US">A</span>项。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140D1;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">12</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">C<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：内联函数具有程序代码少、频繁调用和执行效率高的特征，所以选择<span lang="EN-US">C</span>项。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\n新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;\ncolor:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140D1;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">13</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">C<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：<span lang="EN-US">a=4,</span>因为后减，<span lang="EN-US">b</span>的值与<span lang="EN-US">a</span>、<span lang="EN-US">bb</span>相关，<span lang="EN-US">b</span>＝<span lang="EN-US">4*5=20</span>，而与<span lang="EN-US">aa</span>没有任何关系。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140D1;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">14</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">A<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：<span lang="EN-US">extern</span>用于声明外部变量的。<span lang="EN-US">register</span>声明寄存器类型变量。无<span lang="EN-US">cpu</span>类型。它们都不能声明类成员。<span lang="EN-US">public</span>声明为公有访问权限，所以选择<span lang="EN-US">A</span>项。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140D1;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">15</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">B<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：类的定义，如果有自身类对象，使得循环定义，<span lang="EN-US">B</span>项错误。在类中具有自身类的指针，可以实现链表的操作，当然也可以使用对象的引用。类中可以有另一个类的对象，即成员对象。所以选择<span lang="EN-US">B</span>选项。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140D1;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">16</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋体;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#3140D1;mso-font-kerning:0pt">、答案：<span lang="EN-US">D<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:新宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\n新宋体;color:#36824A;mso-font-kerning:0pt">解析：地址作为实参，表示实参与形参代表同一个对象。如果实参是数值，形参也是普通变量，此时形参是实参的备份。所以选择<span lang="EN-US">D</span>项。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-font-family:新宋体;color:#3140d1;mso-font-kerning:0pt\'=""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align:left;layout-grid-mode:char;\nmso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:新宋